19jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 8068 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35872,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/shaytan-out-of-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":35870,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Baqarah keeps Satan out of home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, everything has a summit and the summit of the Quran is Surat al-Baqarah. Whoever recites it in his house at night, Satan will not enter his house for three nights. Whoever recites it during\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32701,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/06\/two-ayat-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35870,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Al-Baqarah decree before heaven and earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah issued a decree two thousand years before He created the heavens and the earth. He sent down two verse for the end of Surat al-Baqarah. They are not recited in a house but that Satan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35874,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/shaytan-surah-al-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35870,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Satan does not enter with Surat al-Baqarah recited","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRecite Surat al-Baqarah in your houses, for Satan does not enter a house in which Surat al-Baqarah is recited.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2162 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/ali-three-baqarah-before-bed\/","url_meta":{"origin":35870,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Quran: Recite last three verses of al-Baqarah before bed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI have not seen anyone of intelligence go to sleep until he had recited these three verses at the end of Surat al-Baqarah.\u201d Source: Sunan al